#
# Test of # and % syntax
#
IN 
FIN                                         9
FIN                                         2 A             10
FIN                                         2 D             10
FIN                                         5
FIN # Comment line
FIN # A very long comment line with very many words
FIN #A-very-long-comment-line-with-lots-and-lots-of-words
FIN                                           A1    10D1
FIN %      40H0
FIN                                                   J154
FIN                                                   J156
FIN        Left comment                               J155
FIN                                                   J154          and right
FIN                                                   J157
FIN                                                   J155  0
FIN                                           D1   +21HELLO
FIN                                         5         A1
OUT                                         9
OUT                                         2 A0            10
OUT                                         2 D0            10
OUT                                         5
OUT  Comment line                           1
OUT  A very long comment line with very     1 many words
OUT A-very-long-comment-line-with-lots-and-l1 ots-of-words
OUT                                           A1    10D1
OUT                                                 40H0
OUT                                                   J154
OUT                                                   J156
OUT        Left comment                               J155
OUT                                                   J154          and right
OUT                                                   J157
OUT                                                   J155  0
OUT                                           D1   +21HELLO
OUT                                         5         A1
OUT 
#
# Test of data term output format
#
IN 
FIN                                         5       01
FIN                                           D1    01 34     7
FIN                                                +015     1234
FIN                                                -01  7      89
FIN                                                 01        17
FIN                                                +21TT
FIN                                                -21TESTTEST
FIN                                                 21Q
FIN                                                 21
FIN                                                 31 GRONK
OUT                                         5       01
OUT                                           D1    01   34  0007
OUT                                                +01    5  1234
OUT                                                -01    7  0089
OUT                                                 01         17
OUT                                                +21TT
OUT                                                -21TESTT
OUT                                                 21Q
OUT                                                 21
OUT                                                 31
OUT
ERR **Error: Unknown data term type 31, line 10.
ERR **Error: Only integer and string data terms have been implemented.
ERR 
